getPriceDateListIterator

public java.util.ListIterator getPriceDateListIterator(boolean desc)
Get the all of the Price date keys in a ListIterator format for forwards and backwards traversal of the list. A descending list will begin at the most current date and should be traversed backwards (previous). An ascending list (desc = false) will begin at the earliest available date and should be traversed forwards (next). This ListIterator cannot have objects added or removed from it.

Returns:
the ListIterator of keys.
